Module kivakit.resource
Package com.telenav.kivakit.filesystem.spi

Interface FileSystemObjectService

All Superinterfaces:
ByteSized, ModificationTimestamped, ResourcePathed
All Known Subinterfaces:
FileService, FolderService
public interface FileSystemObjectService extends ByteSized, ModificationTimestamped, ResourcePathed
A service provider interface (SPI) common to all filesystem objects. Implementers must provide:
  • chmod(PosixFilePermission...) - Changes permissions of the object
  • exists() - True if the object exists
  • delete() - Deletes the object
  • isFolder() - Returns true if the object is a folder
  • parent() - The parent FolderService of the object, if any
  • path() - The path to the object on the filesystem
  • root() - The root folder
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
See Also:
FileService, FolderService
